---
/* src/components/AgeGroups.astro */
---
<section id="programmes" class="age-groups">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-title">
      <h2>Programmes <span class="text-primary">Tailored for Growth</span></h2>
      <p>Children grow differently at different stages — and we respect that.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="groups-grid">
      <!-- Ages 3-5 -->
      <div class="group-card">
        <div class="icon-floating soccer float"></div>
        <div class="group-header">
            <span class="age-tag">Ages 3-5</span>
            <h3>The Discovery Stage</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="group-desc">These are the years when children first learn to trust their bodies.</p>
        <ul class="features">
          <li>Build confidence to try new activities</li>
          <li>Learn simple routines & instructions</li>
          <li>Enjoy being active in a group</li>
          <li>Feel comfortable with movement</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Ages 6-9 -->
      <div class="group-card featured">
        <div class="icon-floating shoe float" style="animation-delay: -2s;"></div>
        <div class="group-header">
            <span class="age-tag">Ages 6-9</span>
            <h3>The Foundational Stage</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="group-desc">At this age, children begin to understand effort, rules, and teamwork.</p>
        <ul class="features">
          <li>Developing physical confidence</li>
          <li>Understanding discipline & consistency</li>
          <li>Learning how to cooperate with others</li>
          <li>Discovering interest in sports</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Ages 10-12 -->
      <div class="group-card">
        <div class="icon-floating trophy float" style="animation-delay: -4s;"></div>
        <div class="group-header">
            <span class="age-tag">Ages 10-12</span>
            <h3>The Excellence Stage</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="group-desc">These years shape confidence for life and leadership skills.</p>
        <ul class="features">
          <li>Build stamina and physical control</li>
          <li>Learn responsibility & self-discipline</li>
          <li>Develop leadership & teamwork</li>
          <li>Gain confidence to try new challenges</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .age-groups {
    background-color: var(--color-surface);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .section-title {
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .groups-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  .group-card {
    background: var(--color-bg);
    padding: 4rem 2rem 3rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
    position: relative;
  }

  .icon-floating {
    position: absolute;
    top: -3rem;
    left: 2rem;
    width: 100px;
    height: 100px;
    background-image: url('/playplex-website/images/icons.png');
    background-size: 260%;
    background-color: #1a2333; /* Dark background to blend better */
    border-radius: 50%; /* Make them circular emblems */
    border: 4px solid var(--play-yellow); /* Fun border */
    box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
    z-index: 10;
  }

  /* Sprite positions based on the 1024x1024 layout */
  .soccer { background-position: 5% 10%; border-color: var(--play-orange); }
  .shoe { background-position: 95% 10%; border-color: var(--play-blue); }
  .trophy { background-position: 50% 95%; border-color: var(--play-yellow); }

  .group-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-10px);
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .group-card.featured {
    border: 1px solid var(--color-primary);
    background: linear-gradient(145deg, var(--color-bg) 0%, rgba(247, 134, 61, 0.02) 100%);
    box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }

  .age-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.5rem 1.25rem;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    border-radius: 99px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  .featured .age-tag {
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: #000;
  }

  h3 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .group-desc {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .features {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    margin-top: auto;
  }

  .features li {
    font-size: 1rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1rem;
    color: #cbd5e1;
  }

  .features li::before {
    content: '✦';
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  @media (max-width: 1100px) {
    .groups-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 5rem;
      padding-top: 2rem;
    }
    .group-card.featured {
      transform: scale(1);
    }
  }
</style>
